---
title: Creamy White Wine Mussel Tagliatelle  with Cheesy Garlic Baguette and Balsamic Dressed Salad
description: This Creamy White Wine Mussel Tagliatelle takes inspiration from classic restaurant dishes to bring a fine dining experience straight into your home!

Say hello to a fresh ingredient - mussels! These tiny but delicious shellfish are famous for their pincer-like shells. Dressed in a white wine and garlic reduction, these mussels are worth flexing about!
